animation_saver         Retrieve a function for saving animations based
                        on a string/function or a filename
auto_browse             Auto browse to a filename
gganimate               Show an animation of a ggplot2 object
gganimate_save          Save a gganimate object to a file
gganimate_tempfile      Create a temporary file within the temporary
                        directory
plot_ggplot_build       Plot a built ggplot object
print.gganimate         Print a gganimate object, allowing browsing in
                        RStudio
